### What Step 2 Did

**Output Table Schema:**

| Column | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| customer_id | Unique customer identifier |
| year_month | Calendar month (YYYY-MM) |
| breadth_score | Count of distinct departments purchased from |
| total_spend | Sum of net transaction amounts |
| visit_count | Number of distinct transactions (store trips) |
